<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Hi there,</h4>

    <p>Here is an update on <%= @child.first_name %>'s <%=  Behaviour::CATEGORIES[@behaviour.category] %> development:</p>
    <p><%= @child.first_name %> is currently <span style="font-weight: bold"><%= @behaviour.title_present %></span>.</p>


    <p>Here are recommended types of PLAY to boost this important development:</p>
    <ul>
      <% @behaviour.activities.each do |activity| %>
        <li><a href="<%= play_children_url(:aid => activity.id, :no => 1) %>"><%= @child.replace_forms(activity.title).html_safe %></a> - <%= @child.replace_forms(activity.description_short).html_safe %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Here are some upcoming <%=  Behaviour::CATEGORIES[@behaviour.category] %> behaviors to WATCH for:</p>
    <% @next_two_behaviours.each_with_index do |behaviour,index| %>
      <%= " and " if index > 0 %><%= link_to @behaviour.title_present, watch_children_url(:bid => behaviour.id) %>
    <% end %>    

    <p>Remember, you can always get a current summary of <%= @child.first_name %>'s development by visiting the <%= link_to "Reflect", child_reflect_children_url  %> section. Feel free to record and brag about the awesome things your baby is doing by posting to the <%= link_to "Timeline", show_timeline_url(:child_id => @child.id) %>.  Don't worry, <%= @child.first_name %>'s Timeline is private and only viewable to those you invited.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please email us at <a href="mailto:tickets@baby1.uservoice.com">tickets@baby1.uservoice.com</a>.</p>

    <p>Best,</p>
    <p>BabyFolio Team</p>
    <br/><br/>

  <br/>
  <br/>

  <%= render :partial => 'unsubscribe' %>

  </body>
</html>





